Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,VEARN, THE DARK KING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Flora, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona's Minakator spell\Nwas holding it in check,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but the low rumbling\Nfrom Ban Palace never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, it's completely stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and the others must have destroyed\Na central part of Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whoa!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Hero's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not through yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean\Nthe Dark King was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ban Palace\Nhas been left nonfunctional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lands will no longer be attacked\Nby the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing as it isn't falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Palace itself must be made of\Nmaterial that floats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rather than falling...\Nit looks like it's rising.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Very slowly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little by little.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Crests on your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, in my left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just Master or Larhart\Nwho helped me from beyond death!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father becoming a Crest and living on\Ninside you sounds too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you seem so happy, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's that...!\N-Goroa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was Goroa, the Drumbler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that drum monster\Nis what a Drumbler really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that Ban gave him power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But can Ban really transform\Nsuch a small monster like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't surprise me if he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His Magic Power is unfathomable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! To the top of\Nthe Tower of Supremacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But the stairs and everything\Nwere blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The back of his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's unbelievably tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He fought Ron Berku, then me and Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been fighting all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet he doesn't seem tired at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hit him\Nwith several mortal blows already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my weapon that's damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only assume he's taken no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be hit by attacks,\Nand I can't be damaged by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight seems balanced,\Nbut the results are obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right. If we fight for too long...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we'll get exhausted,\Nallowing Mystban to strike us and win.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to uncover the secret\Nto his invulnerability.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even my attacks\Ncan kill him like this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the dome that was\Non top of the Tower of Supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the castle above it\Nwas blown away by your Doru Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doru Aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It truly is a powerful spell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that\Nmaybe it took out Ban, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He might have taken\Nsome damage from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's much stronger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, Leona!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ban!\N-That's him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations in blowing away my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to hold back any longer\Nif you're capable of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall erase you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Ban, the Dark King?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ban's always been relaxed,\Nbut now I sense open malice!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ban's coming at us at full strength!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simply unleashing his Magic Power\Ncreates this much force?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Ban at full power!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he defeated me last time,\Nhe was barely even trying!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I stand a chance against him?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may have powered up with two Crests,\Nbut my current strength...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"Can I really match him\Nwith my two Crests?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin Dragon Crests.\NThat is what I call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Twin Dragon Crests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Dragon Knight's life ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,their Crest is passed on to the new life\Nthat resides inside the Mother Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The danger posed by a Dragon Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is largely due to the Combat Instincts\Ncontained within the Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Dragon Crest contains{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the collective skill of Dragon Knights\Naccumulated over centuries.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that is passed on to the next Knight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon Knights are born with\Nthe battle skills of past Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're combat geniuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the son of Baran, a Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your own strength,\Nbut you did not inherit the skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's Crest\Nhas been passed down properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It has given you super combat abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,completing the Twin Dragon Crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,With your innate strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the combat experience of past\NDragon Knights, a Super Knight was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you are that Super Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer predict your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You may surpass even the Dragonoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Dark King Ban,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,believe I have nothing to fear\Nin the Trio of Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But the unpredictable\Ncannot be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediate annihilation!\NThat is my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.44,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGA STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:08.45,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}KAISER PHOENIX{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediate annihilation!\NThat is my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Leona, stay back for now!\N-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed his warnings, Princess of Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To approach means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, nothing can be done\Nagainst this strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to fight back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast! And the impact's\Nway stronger than before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! What's wrong?! Fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. He must not be able to make\Nhis first strike yet!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ban once broke his sword.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And his Doru Aura didn't affect him at all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's freezing up\Nand can't get a handle on how to fight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-How do I fight?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my sword? Or with spells?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Has fear taken you?\NDisappointing, but convenient for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-How do I fight?!{\i}\N-Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to overthink it!\NJust punch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell! The Dark King Ban fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to get in the first hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!\NOverthinking will just hold me back!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could never beat him\Nby fighting normally!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only option's been to hit him\Nwith my all and find an opening!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leona was trying to tell me that!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona! Thanks for the great advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a little improper for a princess\Nto tell someone to punch somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on!\NI was trying to help you loosen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believed I had him... but I didn't.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's movements...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His unpredictable movements...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:16:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's inherited the years of\NCombat Instincts from the Dragon Knights!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Just attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit him with everything!\NAll of my best attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Earth Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Little whelp! You underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It won't break?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Earth Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's amazing, Dai!\NYou're evenly matched with the Dark King!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's working! I can fight!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Dragonic Aura, power, and speed...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all far beyond\Nwhat they were with one Crest!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like my body isn't my own!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew he was this powerful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since he unleashed his Doru Aura.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's likely that Dragon Knights\Ncan only cast Doru Aura in Dragonoid form{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because their normal forms can't\Nwithstand the power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why they have to transform\Ninto the Dragonoid form to use the spell.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like a built-in safety function.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he used it just as he is.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai's power is equal to\Nthat of the Dragonoid, or even stronger.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm interested in\Nisn't that power on the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This attack will reveal\Nwhat I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Calamity Wall!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike before, this is\Nmy Calamity Wall at full strength!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's fast! I can't dodge it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Aura!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's something similar to Aura!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's blasting upwards\Nwhile approaching at high speed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He passed through it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through the force of the Calamity Wall!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These shocks...\NKing Ban has engaged with Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, heal Larhart before he tires out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but he's the only one\Nwho can match Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Popp!\N-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to learn.\NYou're not strong enough to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the second time\NI've protected you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-You?!\N-He's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He overcame death and was reborn\Nas our new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel! You're all right!\NThank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What... What do you mean, "Don't worry"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was... I mean\Nwe were worried sick about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go off on your own again,\NI swear I'll kick your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I doubt I'll need to do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Backup is here\Nand our enemies are limited in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if he withstood it\Nwith his Dragonic Aura...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he would have taken heavy damage\Nfrom the shockwave.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}by shielding himself with a Dragonic Aura\Nsimilar in nature to my Calamity Wall,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he passed through\Nwithout being affected by the shockwave.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only Dai himself,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but none of his friends have ever\Nshown such skill and inventiveness.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure of it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Combat Instincts passed down{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}among Dragon Knights\Nsince the time of the gods{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}have begun to take root within him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai thwarts Ban's Calamitous Wall{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and fights with skills\Nthat rival or even surpass the Dark King.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Aban and Kilban's duel\Ngrows ever more intense.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban grows angry at Kilban's cruelty,\Nwhile Kilban remains eerily calm.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.21,0:23:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually, their duel\Nreaches its conclusion.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Kilban's Trap"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:23:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:01.89,On Top,,0,0,0,,
